programme.title: The Scorpion King
programme.desc: In this prequel to the blockbuster Mummy films, a mercenary is hired by a dissident alliance to kill the beautiful sorceress Cassandra, from whom the brutal tyrant Memnon draws his strength. Once Cassandra is removed the alliance plans to face Memnons armies on their own terms, but the sorceress is not all she seems in this swirling, CGI-laden romp.

programme.title: Men in Black
programme.desc: Men in Black follows the exploits of Agents Kay and Jay, members of a top-secret organization established to monitor alien activity on Earth. The two MIB find themselves in the middle of a deadly plot by an intergalactic terrorist, who has arrived on Earth to assassinate two ambassadors from opposing galaxies. Kay and Jay face a simple imperative: track down the interloper or Earth will be destroyed. Its all in a days work for the Men in Black.

programme.title: Doomsday
programme.desc: This futuristic action thriller relates the details of the spread of the highly infectious Reaper virus, which resulted in the erection of a 30-foot-high wall of reinforced steel to block off the top area of the United Kingdom. More than 25 years later, with a new strain of the virus now threatening an overcrowded London, Major Eden Sinclair is sent to the infected zone to find a cure. Upon arrival, she finds herself confronted by a population gone wild, descended into utter savagery and cannibalism.

programme.title: The Mummy (1999)
programme.desc: Adventurer Rick OConnell and Egyptologist Evelyn Carnahan discover the lost city of Hamunaptra, and struggle to save the world from unspeakable evil after they inadvertently stumble upon a mummys tomb in 1923, and the mummy is accidentally resurrected.

programme.title: The Mummy Returns
programme.desc: When a chain of events finds the corpse of Imhotep resurrected in the British Museum, the mummy walks the Earth once more, determined to fulfil his quest for immortality. An even more powerful force born of the darkest rituals of ancient Egypt has also been set loose in the world. When these two forces clash, the fate of the world will hang in the balance, sending the OConnells on a desperate race to save the world.

programme.title: Morbius
programme.desc: Biochemist Dr Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.

programme.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
programme.desc: When an Army Major is framed for treason, Reacher discovers shes the target of a massive government conspiracy and risks everything to take down the corrupt organisation.

programme.title: World War Z
programme.desc: The story revolves around United Nations employee Gerry Lane, who traverses the world in a race against time to stop a pandemic that is toppling armies and governments and threatening to decimate humanity itself.

programme.title: Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit
programme.desc: Based on the character created by bestselling author Tom Clancy, Jack Ryan is a global action thriller set in the present day. This original story follows a young Jack as he uncovers a financial terrorist plot. The story follows him from 9/11, through his tour of duty in Afghanistan, which scarred him forever, and into his early days in the Financial Intelligence Unit of the modern CIA where he becomes an analyst, under the guardianship of his handler, Harper. When Ryan believes hes uncovered a Russian plot to collapse the United States economy, he goes from being an analyst to becoming a spy and must fight to save his own life and those of countless others, while also trying to protect the thing thats more important to him than anything, his relationship with his fiancee Cathy.

programme.title: Sucker Punch
programme.desc: This film is an epic action fantasy that takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, and her incredible adventures blur the lines between whats real and what is imaginary. She has been locked away against her will, but Babydoll has not lost her will to survive. Determined to fight for her freedom, she urges four other young girls - the reluctant Sweet Pea, the outspoken Rocket, the street-smart Blondie and the fiercely loyal Amber - to band together and try to escape a terrible fate at the hands of their captors, Blue and Madam Gorski, before the mysterious High Roller comes for Babydoll. Led by Babydoll, the girls engage in fantastical warfare against everything from samurais to serpents, with a virtual arsenal at their disposal. Together, they must decide what they are willing to sacrifice in order to stay alive. But with the help of a Wise Man, their unbelievable journey - if they succeed - will set them free.

programme.title: Blade
programme.desc: Before Blades mother gave birth to him, she was bitten by a vampire, which made Blade immune to vampires. Now a vampire hunter, Blade, joined by vampire detective Hannibal King and Dracula-descendent Frank Drake, slay vampires.

programme.title: Black Hawk Down
programme.desc: A harrowing war drama where two Black Hawk helicopters are shot down over Mogadishu, trapping an elite team of American soldiers in a 15-hour firefight as they try to recover their fallen comrades.

programme.title: Venom
programme.desc: Eddie Brock is a broken man after he loses everything including his job and fiancee. programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout

programme.title: Doom

programme.title: The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor
programme.desc: The OConnells must stop a mummy awoken from a 2000-year-old curse who threatens to plunge the world into his merciless, unending service. Doomed by a wronged sorceress, Zi Yuan, to spend eternity in suspended animation, the ruthless Dragon Emperor and his 10,000 warriors have laid forgotten for eons, entombed in clay as a vast, silent Terracotta Army.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
programme.desc: On a dangerous assignment to recover stolen plutonium, Ethan Hunt chooses to save his team over completing the mission, allowing nuclear weapons to fall into the hands of a deadly network of highly-skilled operatives intent on destroying civilization. Now, with the world at risk, Ethan and his IMF team are forced to become reluctant partners with a hard-hitting CIA agent as they race against time to stop the nuclear fallout. Theres never been a threat more destructive, stunts so jaw-dropping in the film critics are calling the best "Mission" yet!

programme.title: The Huntsman: Winters War
programme.desc: Evil Queen Ravenna betrays her good sister, Freya, with an unforgivable act, freezing Freyas heart of love and unleashing in her an icy power she never knew she possessed. Retreating to a kingdom far to the north, Freya raises an army of Huntsmen as her protectors, with the only rule that no two of them should ever fall in love.

programme.title: Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
programme.desc: Fearing the actions of a god-like superhero left unchecked, Gotham Citys own formidable, forceful vigilante takes on Metropoliss most revered, modern-day saviour, while the world wrestles with what sort of hero it really needs. With Batman and Superman at war with one another, a new threat quickly arises, putting mankind in greater danger than its ever known before.

programme.title: The Scorpion King
programme.desc: In this prequel to the blockbuster Mummy films, a mercenary is hired by a dissident alliance to kill the beautiful sorceress Cassandra, from whom the brutal tyrant Memnon draws his strength. Once Cassandra is removed the alliance plans to face Memnons armies on their own terms, but the sorceress is not all she seems in this swirling, CGI-laden romp.

programme.title: Men in Black

Kay and Jay face a simple imperative: track down the interloper or Earth will be destroyed. Its all in a days work for the Men in Black.

programme.title: Doomsday
programme.desc: This futuristic action thriller relates the details of the spread of the highly infectious Reaper virus, which resulted in the erection of a 30-foot-high wall of reinforced steel to block off the top area of the United Kingdom. More than 25 years later, with a new strain of the virus now threatening an overcrowded London, Major Eden Sinclair is sent to the infected zone to find a cure. Upon arrival, she finds herself confronted by a population gone wild, descended into utter savagery and cannibalism.

programme.title: The Mummy (1999)
programme.desc: Adventurer Rick OConnell and Egyptologist Evelyn Carnahan discover the lost city of Hamunaptra, and struggle to save the world from unspeakable evil after they inadvertently stumble upon a mummys tomb in 1923, and the mummy is accidentally resurrected.

programme.title: The Mummy Returns
programme.desc: When a chain of events finds the corpse of Imhotep resurrected in the British Museum, the mummy walks the Earth once more, determined to fulfil his quest for immortality. An even more powerful force born of the darkest rituals of ancient Egypt has also been set loose in the world. When these two forces clash, the fate of the world will hang in the balance, sending the OConnells on a desperate race to save the world.

programme.title: Morbius
programme.desc: Biochemist Dr Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.

programme.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
programme.desc: When an Army Major is framed for treason, Reacher discovers shes the target of a massive government conspiracy and risks everything to take down the corrupt organisation.

programme.title: World War Z
programme.desc: The story revolves around United Nations employee Gerry Lane, who traverses the world in a race against time to stop a pandemic that is toppling armies and governments and threatening to decimate humanity itself.

programme.title: Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit
programme.desc: Based on the character created by bestselling author Tom Clancy, Jack Ryan is a global action thriller set in the present day. This original story follows a young Jack as he uncovers a financial terrorist plot. The story follows him from 9/11, through his tour of duty in Afghanistan, which scarred him forever, and into his early days in the Financial Intelligence Unit of the modern CIA where he becomes an analyst, under the guardianship of his handler, Harper. When Ryan believes hes uncovered a Russian plot to collapse the United States economy, he goes from being an analyst to becoming a spy and must fight to save his own life and those of countless others, while also trying to protect the thing thats more important to him than anything, his relationship with his fiancee Cathy.

programme.title: Sucker Punch
programme.desc: This film is an epic action fantasy that takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, and her incredible adventures blur the lines between whats real and what is imaginary. She has been locked away against her will, but Babydoll has not lost her will to survive. Determined to fight for her freedom, she urges four other young girls - the reluctant Sweet Pea, the outspoken Rocket, the street-smart Blondie and the fiercely loyal Amber - to band together and try to escape a terrible fate at the hands of their captors, Blue and Madam Gorski, before the mysterious High Roller comes for Babydoll. Led by Babydoll, the girls engage in fantastical warfare against everything from samurais to serpents, with a virtual arsenal at their disposal. Together, they must decide what they are willing to sacrifice in order to stay alive. But with the help of a Wise Man, their unbelievable journey - if they succeed - will set them free.

programme.title: Blade

programme.title: Pixels

programme.title: Dr. Seuss the Lorax
programme.desc: Dr. Seuss The Lorax is an adaptation of Dr. Seuss classic tale of a forest creature who shares the enduring power of hope. In the walled city of Thneed-Ville, where everything is artificial and even the air is a commodity, a boy named Ted hopes to win the heart of his dream girl, Audrey. When he learns of her wish to see a real tree, Ted seeks out the Once-ler, a ruined old businessman outside of town in a stark wasteland. Upon hearing of how the hermit gave into his greed for profits and devastated the land over the protests of the Lorax, Ted is inspired to undo the disaster. However, the greedy Mayor of Thneed-Ville, Aloysius OHare, has made his fortune exploiting the environmental collapse and is determined to stop the boy from undermining his business.

programme.title: The Flintstones

programme.title: Shrek Forever After
programme.desc: In the final chapter of this popular animation franchise, Mike Myers voices Shrek, who is not scaring villagers away like he used to, but now agrees to autograph pitch forks. Longing for the days when he felt like a real ogre, Shrek is duped into signing a pact with the smooth-talking deal-maker, Rumpelstiltskin (Walt Dohrn). Shrek now finds himself in a twisted, alternate version of Far Far Away, where ogres are hunted, Rumpelstiltskin is king and Shrek and Fiona (Cameron Diaz) have never met. Shrek must undo all hes done in the hope of saving his friends, restoring his world and reclaiming his one true love.

programme.title: Pixels
programme.desc: As kids in the 1980s, Sam Brenner, Will Cooper, Ludlow Lamonsoff, and Eddie The Fire Blaster Plant saved the world thousands of times - at 25 cents a game in the video arcades. Now, theyre going to have to do it for real. When intergalactic aliens discover video feeds of classic arcade games and misinterpret them as a declaration of war, they attack the Earth, using the video games as the models for their assaults, and now, US President Cooper must call on his old-school arcade friends to save the world from being destroyed by PAC-MAN, Donkey Kong, Galaga, Centipede, and Space Invaders. Joining them is Lt Col Violet Van Patten, a specialist supplying the arcaders with unique weapons to fight the aliens.

programme.title: Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen
programme.desc: When college-bound Sam Witwicky learns the truth about the ancient origins of the Transformers, he must accept his destiny and join Optimus Prime and Bumblebee in their epic battle against the Decepticons, who have returned stronger than ever with a plan to destroy our world.

programme.title: Dr. Seuss the Lorax
programme.desc: Dr. Seuss The Lorax is an adaptation of Dr. Seuss classic tale of a forest creature who shares the enduring power of hope. In the walled city of Thneed-Ville, where everything is artificial and even the air is a commodity, a boy named Ted hopes to win the heart of his dream girl, Audrey. When he learns of her wish to see a real tree, Ted seeks out the Once-ler, a ruined old businessman outside of town in a stark wasteland. Upon hearing of how the hermit gave into his greed for profits and devastated the land over the protests of the Lorax, Ted is inspired to undo the disaster. However, the greedy Mayor of Thneed-Ville, Aloysius OHare, has made his fortune exploiting the environmental collapse and is determined to stop the boy from undermining his business.

programme.title: The Flintstones
programme.desc: Travel back to the stone-age in this big-budget treatment of the worlds favourite prehistoric family! Fred Flintstone, a put-upon blue-collar worker struggling to squeak by, with the help of his best buddy Barney and his wife Wilma. After an aptitude test mix up, Fred Flintstone trades his job as Slate and Company Bronto-crane operator for a vice presidency. But theres trouble brewing in Bedrock: An evil executive and his sinister secretary are now plotting to use Fred as the fall guy in an embezzlement scheme!

programme.title: Tad The Lost Explorer
programme.desc: Due to a fortuitous mix-up, Tad, a dreamy construction worker, is mistaken for a famous archaeologist and sent on an expedition to Peru. With the help of Jeff, his faithful dog, an intrepid teacher, a mute parrot and a hustler, they will try to save the mythical Lost City of the Incas from an evil band of treasure hunters.

programme.title: Spirit: Stallion of the Cimarron
programme.desc: A tale which follows the adventures of a wild and rambunctious mustang stallion as he journeys through the untamed American frontiers, encountering man for the first time, Spirit defies being broken, even as he develops a remarkable friendship with a young Lakota brave named Little Creek. The young stallion also finds love with a beautiful paint mare named Rain on his way to becoming one of the greatest unsung heroes of the Old West.

programme.title: Wallace and Gromit: Curse Of Were-Rabbit
programme.desc: Wallace and Gromits latest enterprise is Anti-Pesto, pest control with a heart. When called upon by the dotty Lady Tottington to solve her rabbit infestation, Wallace tangles with her Ladyships would-be suitor, rotten cad Victor Quartermaine. At first Wallace and Gromit seem to have things in hand. But Wallaces mind transference device malfunctions, and hes in danger of being bagged by Quartermaine. Wallace teeters perilously close to disaster and his four-legged pal, Gromit, faces almost insurmountable odds to save the day!

programme.title: Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie
programme.desc: George and Harold are fourth-grade BFFs who love dreaming up funny pranks. One day, they accidentally hypnotise their principal into believing hes a dimwitted hero named Captain Underpants. But when the new schoolteacher turns out to be a disgraced scientist bent on ridding the world of laughter, George, Harold and Captain Underpants must band together to stop his evil agenda.

programme.title: Richard the Stork and the Mystery of ...
programme.desc: Little sparrow Richard meets a flock of sparrows who are being held captive by the peacock Zamano. To regain their freedom, they have to go on a great adventure together and find a mysterious treasure.

programme.title: Mr. Peabody and Sherman
programme.desc: Mr Peabody, the most accomplished dog in the world, and his mischievous boy Sherman, use their time machine - the WABAC - to go on the most outrageous adventures known to man or dog. But when Sherman takes the WABAC out for a joyride to impress his friend Penny, they accidentally rip a hole in the universe, wreaking havoc on the most important events in world history. Before they forever alter the past, present and future, Mr. Peabody must come to their rescue, ultimately facing the most daunting challenge of any era: figuring out how to be a parent. Together, the time traveling trio will make their mark on history.

programme.title: Stuart Little 2
programme.desc: Stuart, the Little familys lonely mouse son, gets into strife by befriending a canary.

programme.title: Daddy Day Camp
programme.desc: When the dads expand their childcare magic to Camp Driftwood, serving up sports, crafts and teaching the kids a thing or two about nature, they discover the camp has everything it needs except a plan to put the bullies of rival Camp Canola to shame. With some quick thinking, teamwork, a secret weapon and some off-the-wall crazy antics, the dads and kids unite to make sure Daddy Day Camp secures its rightful place in kid camp history.

programme.title: Sinbad: Legend of the Seven Seas
programme.desc: Its high-seas adventure when legendary swashbuckler Sinbad, his loyal pooch Spike, and the daring Princess Marina face off against the trickster Goddess of Chaos and her mischievous monsters.

programme.title: The Smurfs 2
programme.desc: Evil wizard Gargamel creates a couple of mischievous Smurf-like creatures called the Naughties hoping they will let him harness the magical Smurf-essence. However, he soon discovers that he needs the help of Smurfette, who knows the secret to turning the Naughties into real Smurfs. When Gargamel and his Naughties kidnap Smurfette from Smurf Village and bring her to Paris, its up to Papa, Clumsy, Grouchy and Vanity to reunite with their human friends, Patrick and Grace Winslow, and rescue her!

programme.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
programme.desc: The journey begins when young adventurer Sean receives a coded distress signal from a mysterious island where no island should exist - a place of strange life forms, mountains of gold, deadly volcanoes, and more than one astonishing secret. Unable to stop him from going, Seans new stepfather joins the quest. Together with a helicopter pilot and his beautiful, strong-willed daughter, they set out to find the island, rescue its lone inhabitant and escape before seismic shock waves force the island under the sea and bury its treasures forever.

programme.title: Great Continental Railway Journeys
programme.desc: Follow Michael Portillo as he experiences the thrill of global rail travel, visiting locations recommended by his historic guidebook, and uncovering stories from the past.

programme.title: Ireland: Coast and Country
programme.desc: Theres fine dining seafood from a food truck, and the first native oysters of the season with a Michelin star chef. Will two young seals make it safely back to the wild?

programme.title: Lost in the Woods
programme.desc: The feature doc explores how Kangaroo Islands ill-fated timber industry grew an environmental and economic disaster that has split the community, tainted the highest office in South Australia, and left a growing list of unfolding dangers in its wake; issues of national and international concern given the koala problem and the blue gum infestation of precious native vegetation.

programme.title: The Forever Prisoner
programme.desc: Acclaimed director Alex Gibney tells the chilling story of Abu Zubaydah, the first high-value detainee subjected to the CIAs program of Enhanced Interrogation Techniques (EITs), later identified as torture by those outside the agency.

programme.title: Great Music Cities of the World
programme.desc: Some are inland. Some are by the sea. Some are small towns broken by recession and others are the greatest metropolises the world has ever known. MAX explores the pioneering cities that have shaped music history.

programme.title: Worlds Most Expensive Cruise
programme.desc: The final episode of the series sees the stunning Seven Seas Splendor sailing around the Canary Islands while celebrating the companys 30th anniversary. For Assistant Cruise Director Alex and Social Hostess, Annabel, this means organising a glitzy black and gold themed party for the end of the cruise. But before the voyage can begin, the ship is docked in Gibraltar for the very first time and its fallen to Annabel to give a guided tour to local dignitaries and ensure they will welcome the ship back to port for future cruises. There are plenty of dazzling details Annabel can show off to the VIPs but also a few hitches along the tour, so the ships relationship with Gibraltar hangs in the balance.

programme.desc: The seven contestants who won through in the regional heats face their most daunting challenge yet as they paint a double portrait at the Royal Academy. programme.title: Born to Be King
programme.desc: Reveals the compelling inside story of the extraordinary life of King Charles. The documentary uses unique, unprecedented and unlimited access to a fascinating well of footage to show a definitive story of the man behind the crown, while exploring the direction of the British monarchy under King Charles III.

programme.title: Secrets of the Queens Coronation
programme.desc: A behind-the-scenes look at Queen Elizabeth IIs coronation. This documentary shares memories and anecdotes from people who plays key roles at the celebration, all speaking publicly for the first time.

programme.title: Love Has Won: The Cult of Mother God
programme.desc: Introduces Amys daughter, Madi, who describes her life growing up without a mother. Amy and the Love Has Won commune are kicked out of Hawaii after Amy claims to be Pele, the Hawaiian goddess of fire. Amys health continues to deteriorate and after her death, her followers take her body to Colorado where the compound is raided 12 days later.

programme.title: Haunted Case Files
programme.desc: Investigator George Acosta is called in by his own sister to rid her Texas home of a dark and malevolent spirit that jealously attacks visitors. When teenagers mess around with a spirit board, they mistakenly unleash a demon that threatens to permanently possess investigator Marie Yates. Another investigator spends the night in a church rectory with a dark past and is shocked to witness something evil attack a team member.

programme.title: American Restoration
programme.desc: Rick Dale, one of Pawn Stars most popular experts, runs Las Vegas based Ricks Restorations, a family business that finds, restores and upcycles cool objects ranging from Cadillacs to Coke Machines. The before and after reveals of his work are always highlights, in part because of the history nuggets Rick Dale shares about each object, whether its a barber chair or a gas pump. In this spinoff series, featuring the dynamic characters at Ricks workplace, viewers will watch a variety of objects be bought, bartered and transformed, learning the process of restoration; how do you duplicate Coke machine red? Where can you find 1920s tires? A storyteller who works with tools instead of a pen, Rick shares when and why objects were invented, who used them and how fixing or transforming them changes their value.

programme.title: Pawn Stars
programme.desc: Chumlee is holding out for a superhero when a seller brings in boxes of inherited comic books. Rick learns you have to buy money to make money when some rare, turn-of-the-century currency hits his counter.

programme.title: Pawn Stars
programme.desc: Rick makes an offer to the owner of a bust of Marlon Brando, which turns into a tough call. An 80s Donkey Kong penny bank barrels into the store. Rick spots a cyclops print made by a member of the band Devo.

programme.title: Pawn Stars
programme.desc: The guys make moves on some handwritten math by Albert Einstein. Chumlee tries to have an antique headlamp tester fixed. Corey and Chumlee try buying a prop from "Childs Play." Rick tries to confirm that a pill case belonged to Carole Lombard.

programme.title: Pawn Stars
programme.desc: A seller brings in Disneyland employee costumes to The Gold and Silver. Rick finds a Volkswagen space patrol toy car. Corey sees a rare "Smoking Hamilton" currency printing error. Rick allies himself with an art expert to appraise a WWII painting.

programme.title: Outback Truckers
programme.desc: Steve Grahames been trucking for 46 years, but hes travelling into a new world as a viral pandemic sweeps across the globe. Hes about to set out on a journey that will test him like no other. In 4 days time, Western Australian authorities will close the regional borders and Steves rushing to get ahead of the restrictions. Last year 180,000 hectares of forest and plantations were burntin South West Tasmania laying waste to the logging industry. The Bennetts and their crew need to make up for lost time and money, reaching weekly quotas of 1500 tonnes of timber. Helping keep on target, is Ricky Sutcliffe a 32 year trucking veteran who was one of the volunteers who helped fight last years fires.

programme.title: Ice Cold Catch
programme.desc: When a newly-engaged American defense contractor and a struggling British yacht stewardess leave their thankless jobs behind to pursue highly-paid fishing jobs in Iceland, they discover a whole new realm of larger-than-life characters and unanticipated stakes. programme.title: Whose Line Is It Anyway?
programme.desc: Aisha Tyler hosts another hilarious episode of the legendary improv show featuring regulars Wayne Brady, Ryan Stiles and Colin Mochrie along with guest performer Greg Proops. In a succession of six laugh out loud games, the team don the usual crazy hats, masks and wigs to ask Questions on the beach, then after another anarchic round of Props, Ryan and Colin construct a Wizard of Oz scene between Dorothy and the Tin Man using audience supplied words in Whose Line. This is followed by a fast moving round of Scenes from a Hat featuring unlikely perfume scents, over caffeinated TV shows and things that dont sound right in an angry voice. After a raucous round of Party Quirks where Greg attempts to guess Waynes celebrities being sucked into a black hole, Colins underwear surveyor and Ryans hungry hummingbird, the show ends with a moving Doo Wop paying tribute to Sarah and her fatal vacuuming accident.

programme.title: Whose Line Is It Anyway?
programme.desc: Aisha Tyler hosts another unforgettable episode of the legendary improv show featuring regulars Wayne Brady, Ryan Stiles and Colin Mochrie along with guest performer Gary Anthony Williams. Highlights of an incident packed show include a Sci-Fi movie themed Questions, a fantastic Three Musketeers Sound Effects that must rank as one of the funniest ever followed by an amusing revoicing of an old Western clip in Film Dub. The Scenes from a Hat round features terrible teachers, awful medical ads, Aishas pick up lines and things you can say at the gym but not about your partner. programme.title: Whose Line Is It Anyway?
programme.desc: Aisha Tyler hosts another fun packed episode of the legendary improv show featuring regulars Wayne Brady, Ryan Stiles and Colin Mochrie along with guest performer Heather Anne Campbell. Ryan and Colin use audience suggested lines to act out a Cinderella Whose Line scenario before acting out scenes from a hat including strange psychiatrists and TV shows that shouldnt be sexy. programme.title: Whose Line Is It Anyway?
programme.desc: Aisha Tyler hosts another hilarious episode of the legendary improv show featuring regulars Wayne Brady, Ryan Stiles and Colin Mochrie along with guest performer Jonathan Mangum. Beginning with a seriously weird speed dating event in Questions, the performers move on to a fast moving Jurassic Park scene in Forward Rewind ending where Jonathan falls from the stage and bangs his head. Theres more injury to follow for him as he is hit by collateral in a lively round of Infomercial before taking part on a packed game of Scenes from a Hat where the performers act out strange bath times, bad competitions, jobs that shouldnt be done in the nude and the wrong time to say I love you. The final two games of a jam packed six game show are a brilliant re-voicing of an old movie clip in Film Dub, followed by a mind bending volleyball scene in the always incredible Sideways Scene.

programme.desc: Former CIA assassin Jason Bourne resurfaces just as his former employers are implementing a new program aimed at hunting him down. Now fully recovered from his amnesia, Bourne teams up with Nicky Parsons to uncover the truth behind his fathers death, while simultaneously exacting revenge and evading the government forces hot on his trail.

programme.title: Charlies Angels: Full Throttle
programme.desc: The Angels, three investigative agents (Barrymore, Diaz and Liu) who work for the Charles Townsend Detective Agency, return for another high-octane series of adventures as they investigate the theft of a database of witness protection profiles, after five of the people on the list are murdered. Theyre aided by a new Bosley (Bernie Mac), in an adventure which pits them against a fallen angel (Moore), their old nemesis, the Thin Man (Glover), and others.

programme.title: Smokin Aces
programme.desc: After snitching mob secrets to the FBI, a $1 million contract is put out on Buddy Aces Israel. Now, everybody wants him dead.

programme.title: The Fall Guy
programme.desc: Hes a stuntman, and like everyone in the stunt community, he gets blown up, shot, crashed, thrown through windows and dropped from the highest of heights, all for our entertainment. And now, fresh off an almost career-ending accident, this working-class hero has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job. What could possibly go right?

programme.title: Monkey Man
programme.desc: Inspired by the legend of Hanuman, an icon embodying strength and courage, Monkey Man stars Patel as Kid, an anonymous young man who ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he is beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash. After years of suppressed rage, Kid discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the citys sinister elite. As his childhood trauma boils over, his mysteriously scarred hands unleash an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.

programme.title: Bad Boys: Ride or Die
programme.desc: The worlds favourite Bad Boys are back with their iconic mix of edge-of-your seat action and outrageous comedy, but this time with a twist: Miamis finest are now on the run.

programme.title: The Punisher
programme.desc: Undercover FBI agent Frank Castle (Thomas Jane) is crushed when his wife and children are killed after accidentally witnessing a mafia hit. With nothing left to lose or to live for, Castle becomes The Punisher a one-man judge, jury and executioner who declares open season on criminals throughout America. Based on the Marvel Comics character, the film also stars John Travolta, Laura Harring, Samantha Mathis and Rebecca Romijn.

programme.title: Charlies Angels (2019)
programme.desc: In this next generation, the worlds most highly trained women all over the globe are now teams of Angels guided by multiple Bosleys taking on the toughest jobs everywhere.

programme.title: Nobody
programme.desc: After failing to fight for his family during a robbery, an unassuming father calls on skills from his hidden past to become a lethal vigilante blazing a wild ride to revenge.

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: An assassin tries to make amends in an effort to restore the sight of a beautiful young singer.

programme.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
programme.desc: When an Army Major is framed for treason, Reacher discovers shes the target of a massive government conspiracy and risks everything to take down the corrupt organisation.

programme.title: Pulp Fiction
programme.desc: Winnfield and Vincent Vega are two hitmen out to retrieve a suitcase stolen from their employer, mob boss Marcellus Wallace. Wallace has also asked Vincent to take his wife Mia out a few days later when Wallace himself will be out of town. Butch Coolidge is an ageing boxer who is paid by Wallace to lose his next fight. Honey Bunny and Pumpkin are a couple of young lovers and small time thieves who decide they need a change of venue. The lives of these seemingly unrelated people are woven together in a wildly entertaining and exhilarating motion picture adventure that both thrills and amuses.

programme.title: Inglourious Basterds
programme.desc: As war rages in Europe, a Nazi-scalping squad of American soldiers, known to their enemy as The Basterds, is on a daring mission to take down the leaders of the Third Reich.

programme.title: Once Upon A Time... In Hollywood
programme.desc: The highly anticipated 9th film from Quentin Tarantino. In 1969 Los Angeles, during the Charles Manson murders, a TV actor and his stunt double, embark on an odyssey to make a name for themselves in the film industry.

programme.title: Sucker Punch
programme.desc: This film is an epic action fantasy that takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, and her incredible adventures blur the lines between whats real and what is imaginary. She has been locked away against her will, but Babydoll has not lost her will to survive. Determined to fight for her freedom, she urges four other young girls - the reluctant Sweet Pea, the outspoken Rocket, the street-smart Blondie and the fiercely loyal Amber - to band together and try to escape a terrible fate at the hands of their captors, Blue and Madam Gorski, before the mysterious High Roller comes for Babydoll. Led by Babydoll, the girls engage in fantastical warfare against everything from samurais to serpents, with a virtual arsenal at their disposal. Together, they must decide what they are willing to sacrifice in order to stay alive. But with the help of a Wise Man, their unbelievable journey - if they succeed - will set them free.

programme.title: Kill
programme.desc: India. When army commando Amrit finds out his true love Tulika is engaged against her will, he boards a New Delhi-bound train in a daring quest to derail the arranged marriage. But when a gang of knife-wielding thieves led by the ruthless Fani begin to terrorize innocent passengers on his train, Amrit takes them on himself in a death-defying kill-spree to save those around him - turning what should have been a typical commute into an adrenaline-fueled thrill ride.

programme.title: Suicide Squad
programme.desc: It feels good to be bad. Assemble a team of the worlds most dangerous, incarcerated supervillains, provide them with the most powerful arsenal at the governments disposal, and send them off on a mission to defeat an enigmatic, insuperable entity. US intelligence officer Amanda Waller has determined only a secretly convened group of disparate, despicable individuals with next to nothing to lose will do. Once they realise they werent picked to succeed, but chosen for their patent culpability when they inevitably fail, will the Suicide Squad resolve to die trying, or decide its everyone for themself?

programme.title: Tango and Cash
programme.desc: Two narcotics detectives cant stand each other. When a crime lord frames them for murder, they have to buddy up to clear their names and put him away.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (2014)
programme.desc: The city needs heroes. Darkness has settled over New York City as Shredder and his evil Foot Clan have an iron grip on everything from the police to the politicians. The future is grim until four unlikely outcast brothers rise from the sewers and discover their destiny as Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. The Turtles must work with fearless reporter April ONeil and her wise-cracking cameraman Vern Fenwick to save the city and unravel Shredders diabolical plan.

programme.desc: Men in Black follows the exploits of Agents Kay and Jay, members of a top-secret organization established to monitor alien activity on Earth. The two MIB find themselves in the middle of a deadly plot by an intergalactic terrorist, who has arrived on Earth to assassinate two ambassadors from opposing galaxies. Kay and Jay face a simple imperative: track down the interloper or Earth will be destroyed. Its all in a days work for the Men in Black.

However, their friendly competition evolves into a bitter rivalry making them fierce enemies-for-life and consequently jeopardising the lives of everyone around them. Full of twists and turns, this film is set against the backdrop of turn-of-the-century London.

programme.title: Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga
programme.desc: As the world fell, young Furiosa is snatched from the Green Place of Many Mothers and falls into the hands of a great biker horde led by the warlord Dementus. Sweeping through the Wasteland, they come across the Citadel presided over by The Immortan Joe. While the two tyrants war for dominance, Furiosa must survive many trials as she puts together the means to find her way home.

programme.title: Morbius
programme.desc: Biochemist Dr Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.

programme.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
programme.desc: When an Army Major is framed for treason, Reacher discovers shes the target of a massive government conspiracy and risks everything to take down the corrupt organisation.

programme.title: World War Z
programme.desc: The story revolves around United Nations employee Gerry Lane, who traverses the world in a race against time to stop a pandemic that is toppling armies and governments and threatening to decimate humanity itself.

programme.title: Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit
programme.desc: Based on the character created by bestselling author Tom Clancy, Jack Ryan is a global action thriller set in the present day. This original story follows a young Jack as he uncovers a financial terrorist plot. The story follows him from 9/11, through his tour of duty in Afghanistan, which scarred him forever, and into his early days in the Financial Intelligence Unit of the modern CIA where he becomes an analyst, under the guardianship of his handler, Harper. When Ryan believes hes uncovered a Russian plot to collapse the United States economy, he goes from being an analyst to becoming a spy and must fight to save his own life and those of countless others, while also trying to protect the thing thats more important to him than anything, his relationship with his fiancee Cathy.

programme.title: Joy Ride
programme.desc: Asian American adoptee Audrey Sullivan is living the dream. Raised in the picturesque small town of White Hills, she has a successful law career, a close relationship with her parents, and her longtime best friend, Lolo, literally lives in her backyard. But Audrey is ready for more. To become a partner at her law firm and leave White Hills behind, she just needs to close one important deal with a client in China. Sounds straightforward enough, until Lolo encourages Audrey to use the trip to locate her birth mother. Oh, and Lolos eccentric cousin, Deadeye, is coming along. So is Kat, a glamorous Chinese soap opera star who roomed with Audrey in college.

programme.title: Ordinary Angels
programme.desc: A struggling hairdresser finds a renewed sense of purpose when she meets a widowed father and his two daughters.

programme.title: Unforgiven
programme.desc: Two retired, down-on-their-luck outlaws pick up their guns one last time to collect a bounty offered by the vengeful prostitutes of the remote Wyoming town of Big Whiskey. English Bob is an ill-fated interloper, a colourful killer-for-hire. There is also the sly and brutal local sheriff, whose brand of law enforcement ranges from unconventional to ruthless. Big trouble is coming to Big Whiskey.

programme.title: Spider-Man: Far From Home
programme.desc: Our friendly neighbourhood Super Hero decides to join his best friends Ned, MJ, and the rest of the gang on a European vacation. However, Peters plan to leave super heroics behind for a few weeks are quickly scrapped when he begrudgingly agrees to help Nick Fury uncover the mystery of several elemental creature attacks, creating havoc across the continent!

programme.title: Morbius
programme.desc: Biochemist Dr Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.

programme.title: Daddys Home
programme.desc: Brad Taggart is a kind-hearted radio executive who wants to be the best possible stepfather to his wifes two children. When her freewheeling ex-husband Dusty breezes back into town, Brads feeling of insecurity quickly develops into an inferiority complex. As Dusty demonstrates his flair for athletics, home repair and bad-boy charisma, Taggart finds himself in a no-holds-barred battle to one-up his rival and win the approval of his family.

programme.title: The Dark Knight Rises
programme.desc: It has been eight years since Batman vanished into the night, turning, in that instant, from hero to fugitive. Assuming the blame for the death of DA Harvey Dent, the Dark Knight sacrificed everything for what he and Commissioner Gordon both hoped was the greater good. For a time the lie worked, as criminal activity in Gotham City was crushed under the weight of the anti-crime Dent Act. Everything will change with the arrival of a cunning cat burglar with a mysterious agenda. Far more dangerous, however, is the emergence of Bane, a masked terrorist whose ruthless plans for Gotham drive Bruce out of his self-imposed exile. Even if he dons the cape and cowl again, Batman may be no match for Bane.

programme.title: Emma.
programme.desc: Jane Austens beloved comedy about finding your equal and earning your happy ending is reimagined in this delicious film adaptation.

programme.title: Ghostbusters: Afterlife
programme.desc: When a single mother and her two kids arrive in a small town, they begin to discover their connection to the original Ghostbusters and the secret legacy their grandfather left behind.

programme.title: The Amazing Spider-Man 2
programme.desc: Spider-Mans greatest battle begins when an evil corporation attempts world domination by deploying an army of super villains to crush Peter Parker.

programme.title: Men in Black
programme.desc: Men in Black follows the exploits of Agents Kay and Jay, members of a top-secret organization established to monitor alien activity on Earth. The two MIB find themselves in the middle of a deadly plot by an intergalactic terrorist, who has arrived on Earth to assassinate two ambassadors from opposing galaxies. Kay and Jay face a simple imperative: track down the interloper or Earth will be destroyed. Its all in a days work for the Men in Black.

programme.title: Snatch
programme.desc: Mickey ONeil, a bare knuckles gypsy fighter, is roped in to save the necks of two small-time operators whose scheming collides with that of a lunatic kingpin villain, Brick Top, and a missing diamond smuggler.

programme.title: Tarot
programme.desc: When a group of friends recklessly violates the sacred rule of Tarot readings, they unknowingly unleash an unspeakable evil trapped within the cursed cards. One by one, they come face to face with fate and end up in a race against death.

programme.title: Emma.

programme.title: The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor
programme.desc: The OConnells must stop a mummy awoken from a 2000-year-old curse who threatens to plunge the world into his merciless, unending service. Doomed by a wronged sorceress, Zi Yuan, to spend eternity in suspended animation, the ruthless Dragon Emperor and his 10,000 warriors have laid forgotten for eons, entombed in clay as a vast, silent Terracotta Army.

programme.title: Hitch
programme.desc: Hitch is a cocky and successful date doctor for the unlucky in love, but when he falls for gossip columnist Sara, he forgets his own rules.

programme.title: Transformers: Age of Extinction
programme.desc: This film begins after an epic battle left a great city torn, but with the world saved. As humanity picks up the pieces, a shadowy group reveals itself in an attempt to control the direction of history, while an ancient, powerful new menace sets Earth in its crosshairs. With help from a new cast of humans, Optimus Prime and the Autobots rise to meet their most fearsome challenge yet. In an incredible adventure, they are swept up in a war of good and evil, ultimately leading to a climactic battle across the world.

programme.title: PowerPoint with Jack Graham
programme.desc: PowerPoint Ministries started as a vision of Dr Jack Graham and his wife, Deb, 20 years ago. They believed that the power of God was evident in their growing church and that His Gospel message should be spread beyond the walls of that church to the world at large. They put their faith into action and purchased airtime on the Trinity Broadcasting Network. PowerPoint Ministries was then officially launched in April 1994. Over the past 19 years, PowerPoint Ministries has grown to an expansive network of local, national, and international television and radio broadcasts. In fact, PowerPoint can be seen or heard by a potential audience of millions of television viewers and radio listeners across the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Iran, Russia, Israel and more. The Ministry has a vision to glorify God by introducing Jesus Christ as Lord to as many people as possible and to develop them in Christian living using the most effective means to impact the world, making an eternal difference in this generation.

Don starts singing along and EMTs confirm he now has a pulse. But Don is not happy and fights his recovery. He was on his way to heaven, and now he has been pulled back, with terrible injuries. As their bond deepens, Autumn realises that moving on doesnt mean forgetting the past - it means opening her heart to new beginnings. But when she discovers Jakes true intentions, she must decide whether to fight for the ranch or take a leap of faith in love once again.

Reeling from the death of her beloved father and the breakup she just suffered, shes ready to focus on moving forward with her life, and channelling all of her energy into getting the new hosting gig on the afternoon talk show at her station. She gets a new assistant, Simone, a beautiful biracial woman who is new in town and so excited to be supporting Monica. They become close quickly, with Simone moving in next door, and engraining herself into Monicas life. But underneath Simones sweet exterior lies a woman who harbors a dark secret, and is determined to become closer than close to Monica, whether she likes it or not! As time goes on, and Simone becomes more and more enmeshed in Monicas life, Monica starts to pick up on the cracks in Simones shiny facade. As she tries to pull back from Simone, Monica and those around her begin to fear that it may be too late - and even worse, that Simone may have had something to do with the death of her father and collapse of her relationship! Monica decides to sever ties with Simone once and for all, however, Simone has other plans. Will Monica get her life back, or will Simone succeed in taking over Monicas life for good?

Oscars resilience to overcome his disability combined with his apparent fairy tale relationship with model Reeva Steenkap turned him into a media favorite. This all shattered one Valentines Day night when four bullets were fired and Reevas life was taken. Her brutal death shocked the world and the court room drama that followed consumed the news.

By the age of 21, Britney Spears already had a number one platinum, debut album, a cover on Rolling Stone, a record-breaking second album, and international superstardom. Success in her personal life, however, would be much harder to achieve. A well-publicized romance and break-up with Justin Timberlake, a three-day marriage to a childhood sweetheart, and an ill-fated marriage to back-up dancer Kevin Federline made for a chaotic contrast to her record-setting music career.

Starting with the 911 call and investigation lead by Detective Steve Thomas, the film provides a closer look into what exactly happened the day after Christmas 1996, when she was found beaten and strangled in the familys basement. With the addition of recently surfaced information, the film takes a fresh look at the events and the competing theories about the murder. Were Patsy and John Ramsey responsible or covering for someone else in the family? Was this a kidnapping gone wrong, or was this the work of a predator who had seen JonBen t in one of her pageants? Twenty years after the tragic events, the question remains: Who killed JonBenet?

Sexy and mysterious, Trey triggers a passion in Tiffanie that she never expected, and suddenly the life shes always planned with Damon is uncertain. But Trey still carries wounds from his history with Damon, and his intentions toward both Tiffanie and Damon are not to be trusted.

programme.desc: Expectant parents become prime suspects in the disappearance of a pregnant woman who was last seen at their garage sale.

programme.title: Non-Stop

programme.title: Girl in Room 13
programme.desc: Grace becomes addicted to opioids after suffering a sports injury. Shes ready to leave her addiction behind under her mothers watch, but Richie kidnaps her to sell her into human trafficking.

programme.title: If There Be Thorns
programme.desc: With Christopher and Cathy Dollanganger living together as man and wife, Cathys two sons are unaware of the incestuous nature of their parents relationship. But when a mysterious woman moves in next door and befriends the younger boy, Bart, he begins a strange transformation and displays accusatory behaviour towards Cathy and Christopher. When Christopher discovers their mysterious neighbour is, in fact, his mother Corrine Dollanganger, all of the familys long-hidden secrets are revealed in a tragic climax.

programme.title: Blonde and Blonder
programme.desc: When two dim-witted blonde bombshells are mistaken for the underworlds most cunning assassins, they are approached with a lucrative contract to take out the head of the Chinese mafia in a globetrotting, air-headed comedy. Two fair-haired beauties have just witnessed a high-profile mob hit, and now the Godfather is convinced that they have what it takes to rub out his most fearsome rival. After accepting a hearty payout and agreeing to carry out the dangerous assignment, the two brainless beauties hit the open road on the adventure of a lifetime.

programme.title: The Pastors Wife
programme.desc: Mary, a dutiful preachers wife and mother of three, becomes the prime suspect in her husbands murder. What went on behind this perfect familys closed doors? Based on a true story.

programme.title: Wedding Planner Mystery
programme.desc: A quirky but lovable event planner makes murder as fun as can be. Homicide doesnt follow our heroine, she seeks it out. Using her circle of contacts, her friendship with a cop and the same research skills that enable her to plan distinctive events - if an unsolved murder occurs in Seattle, Carnegie will find out about it.

programme.title: Michael Jackson: Searching for Neverland
programme.desc: Based on Bill and Javons book Remember the Time: The Last Days of Michael Jackson, this movie will chronicle those intimate moments between Jackson and his children, document the professional turbulence that engulfed Jackson in financial trouble and forced him back to rehearsals for the ill-fated This Is It tour that led to his early death, and help answer the question that fans around the world want to know: What really happened to the King of Pop?

programme.title: Road Trip Hostage
programme.desc: A deranged criminal forces a young woman to drive him across the country.

programme.title: Wife Stalker
programme.desc: Joannas obsessive fantasy of a perfect life with Leo shatters, forcing her to confront harsh reality and the truth about their relationship, with dire consequences.

programme.title: Girl in the Box
programme.desc: In 1977, 22-year-old Colleen Stan doesnt think twice when she hitch hikes and is picked up by a young couple, Cameron and Janice Hooker. But the life she knows is completely ripped away when the couple abducts her and takes her to their home where Cameron tortures and sexually abuses her. For the next seven years, Colleen is imprisoned for up to 23 hours a day, in a coffin-sized box hidden beneath the couples bed. When not incarcerated, Colleen is part of a strange new life as a live-in slave, babysitter, and victim of Camerons bizarre and extreme sexual fantasies.

programme.title: Seeds of Yesterday
programme.desc: The saga of the tormented Dollangangers comes to an end where the family continues to coexist miserably. The film follows Cathys two adult sons, Bart and Jory half-brothers with little in common whose lives are fuelled by deeply troubled relationships, dark secrets and misfortune that come to a head in a way that will haunt the family and its progeny forever.

programme.title: Murdaugh Murders: Part 1
programme.desc: Alex Murdochs familys hidden crimes begin piling up as he attempts to conceal his own financial felonies but falls into a dark spiral.

programme.title: Murdaugh Murders: Part 2
programme.desc: Police rush to the Murdaugh home after Alex Murdaugh reports his wife, Maggie, and son Paul dead. With police and press digging into Alexs life for leads, he attempts to derail their investigation.

programme.title: The Paramedic Who Stalked Me
programme.desc: After a deadly accident, a young woman becomes the target of an obsessed EMT worker who saved her life.

programme.title: Single Black Female
programme.desc: Monica is a young host of one of LAs top morning shows. Reeling from the death of her beloved father and the breakup she just suffered, shes ready to focus on moving forward with her life, and channelling all of her energy into getting the new hosting gig on the afternoon talk show at her station. She gets a new assistant, Simone, a beautiful biracial woman who is new in town and so excited to be supporting Monica. They become close quickly, with Simone moving in next door, and engraining herself into Monicas life. But underneath Simones sweet exterior lies a woman who harbors a dark secret, and is determined to become closer than close to Monica, whether she likes it or not! As time goes on, and Simone becomes more and more enmeshed in Monicas life, Monica starts to pick up on the cracks in Simones shiny facade. As she tries to pull back from Simone, Monica and those around her begin to fear that it may be too late - and even worse, that Simone may have had something to do with the death of her father and collapse of her relationship! Monica decides to sever ties with Simone once and for all, however, Simone has other plans. Will Monica get her life back, or will Simone succeed in taking over Monicas life for good?

programme.title: Oscar Pistorius: Blade Runner Killer
programme.desc: The true story of the sprint runner dubbed theBlade Runner; and his rise to fame as a gold medalist Paralympic champion and as the first double-leg amputee to participate in the Olympics. Oscars resilience to overcome his disability combined with his apparent fairy tale relationship with model Reeva Steenkap turned him into a media favorite. This all shattered one Valentines Day night when four bullets were fired and Reevas life was taken. Her brutal death shocked the world and the court room drama that followed consumed the news.

programme.title: Britney Ever After
programme.desc: This is the tumultuous true story of Britney Jean Spears, one of the bestselling teenage music artists of all-time, whose dating life and public emotional breakdowns were the subjects of a worldwide media frenzy. By the age of 21, Britney Spears already had a number one platinum, debut album, a cover on Rolling Stone, a record-breaking second album, and international superstardom. Success in her personal life, however, would be much harder to achieve. A well-publicized romance and break-up with Justin Timberlake, a three-day marriage to a childhood sweetheart, and an ill-fated marriage to back-up dancer Kevin Federline made for a chaotic contrast to her record-setting music career.

programme.title: Dont Scream, Its Me
programme.desc: Fifteen years ago, Lizs ex-boyfriend, Drew, is caught robbing a bank. Now, hes in her backyard, asking her to hide him after a prison escape.

programme.title: Who Killed JonBenet?
programme.desc: This Lifetime Original Movie revisits the infamous murder of pint-sized beauty queen JonBenet Ramsey and the lurid details that captivated the nation. Starting with the 911 call and investigation lead by Detective Steve Thomas, the film provides a closer look into what exactly happened the day after Christmas 1996, when she was found beaten and strangled in the familys basement. With the addition of recently surfaced information, the film takes a fresh look at the events and the competing theories about the murder. Were Patsy and John Ramsey responsible or covering for someone else in the family? Was this a kidnapping gone wrong, or was this the work of a predator who had seen JonBen t in one of her pageants? Twenty years after the tragic events, the question remains: Who killed JonBenet?

programme.title: Petals on the Wind
programme.desc: A decade after Cathy, Christopher and Carrie escaped from their grandparents attic at Foxworth Hall, the story continues to follow the twisted plight of the family as they attempt to put their sordid past behind them, but soon discover certain secrets cant be left behind. When Cathy finds herself in an abusive relationship with a fellow dancer, Julian, Christopher and Cathy are forced to face the forbidden feelings they developed for one another while coming of age during captivity.

programme.title: Buried in Barstow
programme.desc: Hazel King is a single mother determined to protect her daughter from the life she once had while defending and protecting those who cant protect themselves.

programme.title: Kidnapping in the Grand Canyon
programme.desc: When two best friends hiking the Grand Canyon trust an experienced hiking guide to bring them on an off trail adventure, things go south when he takes them captive, and they have to fight both man and nature to make it out.

programme.title: V.C Andrews Pearl In The Mist
programme.desc: Fate whisked Ruby from a simple life in the Louisiana Bayou. But her new riches bring more treachery than happiness. Even after a year as a Dumas, Ruby still wonders at the splendor of the familys New Orleans mansion and rejoices in the love of the father she had never known. But true happiness in her new home is as elusive as the swamp mist. Ruby must carefully avoid her venomous stepmother, Daphne, while making every effort to befriend her twin sister, Gisselle. While attending Greenwood, the exclusive girls boarding school, Ruby doesnt lose hope in a world that never really wanted her. Ruby will have to summon every last ounce of her Cajun strength to reclaim her home, her future, and the happiness she once knew.

programme.title: Dying For A Crown
programme.desc: Lydia moves to LA with her daughter Elle under mysterious circumstances, becoming the assistant principal at Bellview High where Elle is a senior. With her mother by her side, Elle wont stop to become homecoming queen and gain popularity.

programme.title: Envy: A Seven Deadly Sins Story
programme.desc: Gabrielle Flores has it all - a devoted husband, a beautiful daughter, and one of the best PR firms in the country. But Keisha, who grew up with nothing, wants more than a sisterly bond from Gabrielle - she wants her life, and is willing to do whatever it takes to get it.

programme.title: Unforgiven
programme.desc: Two retired, down-on-their-luck outlaws pick up their guns one last time to collect a bounty offered by the vengeful prostitutes of the remote Wyoming town of Big Whiskey. Big trouble is coming to Big Whiskey.

programme.title: Bad Boys
programme.desc: Two Miami cops must find $100 million in stolen heroin before their department is shut down. With time running out, detectives Burnett and Lowrey track a master thief into the Miami underworld, dodging bullets and bad guys along the way. A sexy witness can identify the suspect, but a mix-up causes her to believe Burnett is Lowrey, forcing the partners to switch identities. Now, between shoot-outs and car chases, married man Burnett has to stick close to their only witness, while playboy Lowrey goes home to his partners wife and kids to learn the joys of parenthood - the hard way.

Can Sherman stop his buff alter ego before its too late, or will Buddy have the last laugh?

But finding Jimmies killer will be no small task - Jimmies loose lips made him a potential target for a laundry list of killers. Lt. Joe Kenda must sort out the hardcore from the wannabes, and convince a reluctant eyewitness to do the right thing. Only then can he tell if Jimmie was killed while fighting crime, or committing it.

programme.title: Homicide Hunter
programme.desc: When a pregnant mother and her two young sons are brutally slain on a quiet weekday afternoon, the city of Colorado Springs is left reeling, and public pressure mounts for the CSPD to catch the cold-blooded monster who did it. After navigating a number of false leads and implementing an exhaustive city-wide manhunt, Kenda learns that the key to finding his killer lies just down the hall from the crime scene itself. With a prime suspect in his sights, Kenda begins to tighten the noose. But what happens next will shock the seasoned detective to his core.

programme.title: Homicide Hunter

Colorado Springs Police face an uphill battle trying to solve a stranger-on-stranger crime, armed with just a composite sketch of the killer and a mysterious bouquet of flowers found at the scene of the crime. In a gruelling investigation that leads from false lead to false lead, Lt. Joe Kendas only hope of solving this one is sheer determination.

programme.title: Homicide Hunter
programme.desc: When shots ring out in the desolate parking lot of a neighbourhood strip club, father of two William Alford, is found dead in the front seat of his pickup truck. Lt. Joe Kenda is tasked with bringing his killer to justice, but after interviewing a number of cagey witnesses, he realises that getting to the truth is easier said than done. As Kenda digs deeper into the case, he uncovers a conspiracy headed by an unlikely leader. With no one willing to cooperate, Kenda must use his formidable interrogation skills to break his suspects down and reveal the shocking truth.

programme.title: Edison
programme.desc: He invented the light bulb, the phonograph, the movie camera, and the nickel-iron-alkaline storage battery. He devised a system for producing synthetic carbolic acid and for wireless telegraph communication between moving trains and stations. By the time of his death, Thomas Alva Edison could lay claim to 1093 successful US patents. But perhaps his greatest invention was himself. Born to a Canadian innkeeper, Edison received his only formal education from his mother at the kitchen table. His first invention was a commercial flop, but by the time he was 35, he had become the nations most prominent celebrity inventor. Tragically, the pace of his work took a terrible toll on his private life. His first wife appears to have killed herself with a lethal dose of morphine; his second was desperately unhappy. And yet, in so many ways, Edison transformed daily life for millions of people and in the process turned himself into the most famous American in the world.

programme.title: Time Team
programme.desc: Tony Robinson doesnt usually get to decide where the team should dig, but in this episode he chooses his first-ever site for investigation: a German anti-aircraft battery built during the Nazis five-year occupation of Jersey. The archaeologists have never investigated anything like this before and must apply all their skills to make sense of a site now reclaimed by a forest. Its soon clear that the gun emplacements are part of a much bigger, complex fortified settlement that was home to hundreds of German soldiers equipped with a vast array of weapons. And, unlike with older sites, the team can talk to people who witnessed life under the occupation firsthand. What emerges is the shocking story of a fortress island where German installations were built by slave labour and the local population began to starve as the war continued. Of terrible conditions that seem more fitting to the eras the team usually investigate rather than just 70 years ago. Over three days, the team uncovers a fascinating and frequently horrifying glimpse of life during war.

programme.desc: The tragic story of the death of a king. September 1513 saw King James IV invade England with the largest and most confident army Scotland had yet seen. programme.title: Edison
programme.desc: He invented the light bulb, the phonograph, the movie camera, and the nickel-iron-alkaline storage battery. He devised a system for producing synthetic carbolic acid and for wireless telegraph communication between moving trains and stations. By the time of his death, Thomas Alva Edison could lay claim to 1093 successful US patents. But perhaps his greatest invention was himself. Born to a Canadian innkeeper, Edison received his only formal education from his mother at the kitchen table. His first invention was a commercial flop, but by the time he was 35, he had become the nations most prominent celebrity inventor. Tragically, the pace of his work took a terrible toll on his private life. His first wife appears to have killed herself with a lethal dose of morphine; his second was desperately unhappy. And yet, in so many ways, Edison transformed daily life for millions of people and in the process turned himself into the most famous American in the world.

programme.title: The First Wives Club
programme.desc: Join Diane Keaton, Bette Midler and Goldie Hawn in this sinfully satisfying revenge romp about a trio of first wives who team up to teach their lying, cheating ex-husbands a lesson. Ivana Trumps galvanising cameo - dont get mad, dahlinks, get everytink - sets the scene in a comedy that hinges on the self-mockery of its ageless stars. programme.title: Single White Female
programme.desc: Hedy Carlson and Allie Jones - two women taken to their most primal extremes from which only one can emerge. When Allie throws out her two-timing boyfriend, Hedy suddenly appears to help her fight off the urges to call him back. The surviving half of a set of twins, Hedy seeks someone to complete her, and sees in the chic and articulate Allie everything she would like to be so she not only moves into the apartment, but into the most personal aspects of Allies life, even going so far as to have her hair styled the same. But when Allie reconciles with her boyfriend, their unspoken bargain goes terrifyingly awry. Instincts dont come baser than this.

programme.desc: Anna Scott is the worlds most famous movie star. Her picture has been plastered on the cover of every magazine, and every time she makes a movie, the entire world knows about it.
